trans-unit.source: Specifies the HTML attributes that an <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.HtmlTextWriter" /> or <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.Html32TextWriter" /> object writes to the opening tag of an HTML element when a Web request is processed.
trans-unit.target: Especifica o atributos HTML que um objeto <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.HtmlTextWriter" /> ou <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.Html32TextWriter" /> grava na marca de abertura de um elemento HTML quando uma solicitação da Web é processada.

trans-unit.source: This enumeration is commonly used with the following methods of the <xref:System.Web.UI.HtmlTextWriter> class: <xref:System.Web.UI.HtmlTextWriter.AddAttribute%2A>, <xref:System.Web.UI.HtmlTextWriter.GetAttributeName%2A>, <xref:System.Web.UI.HtmlTextWriter.IsAttributeDefined%2A>, <xref:System.Web.UI.HtmlTextWriter.RenderBeginTag%2A>.
trans-unit.target: Essa enumeração é comumente usada com os seguintes métodos do <xref:System.Web.UI.HtmlTextWriter> classe: <xref:System.Web.UI.HtmlTextWriter.AddAttribute%2A>, <xref:System.Web.UI.HtmlTextWriter.GetAttributeName%2A>, <xref:System.Web.UI.HtmlTextWriter.IsAttributeDefined%2A>, <xref:System.Web.UI.HtmlTextWriter.RenderBeginTag%2A>.

trans-unit.source: The following example uses the <xref:System.Web.UI.HtmlTextWriterAttribute> enumeration with the <xref:System.Web.UI.HtmlTextWriter.AddAttribute%2A> method to add an `Onclick` attribute to an HTML element and sets its value to ECMAScript code.
trans-unit.target: O exemplo a seguir usa o <xref:System.Web.UI.HtmlTextWriterAttribute> enumeração com o <xref:System.Web.UI.HtmlTextWriter.AddAttribute%2A> método para adicionar um `Onclick` de atributo a um elemento HTML e define seu valor como código ECMAScript.
